    "description": {
      "es": "",
      "en": "There are two supported backends for pdb: 'settrace' and 'monitoring'. See bdb.Bdb for details. The user can set the default backend to use if none is specified when instantiating Pdb. If no backend is specified, the default is 'settrace'. Note breakpoint() and set_trace() will not be affected by this function. They always use 'monitoring' backend. Added in version 3.14."
    },
